WEBVTT

00:02:28.126 --> 00:02:30.971
ak stisnete guličku z fólie

00:02:30.995 --> 00:02:33.093
a stisk uvoľníte.

00:02:33.517 --> 00:02:35.610
(uvoľnenie zovretia guľky z fólie)

00:02:35.869 --> 00:02:37.272
Údery?

00:02:37.296 --> 00:02:38.818
(úder)

00:02:38.842 --> 00:02:40.774
Ups, prehrám to znovu.

00:02:40.798 --> 00:02:41.997
(úder)

00:02:42.535 --> 00:02:46.271
Často vznikajú vrazením noža do zeleniny,

00:02:46.295 --> 00:02:48.137
zvyčajne do kapusty.

00:02:48.661 --> 00:02:50.683
(kapusta prebodnutá nožom)

00:02:50.788 --> 00:02:53.752
Ďalej – lámanie kostí.

00:02:53.776 --> 00:02:56.001
(lámanie kostí)

00:02:56.670 --> 00:02:59.174
Nikto sa naozaj nezranil.

00:02:59.174 --> 00:03:00.978
V skutočnosti ide o...